latestIgtvVideos.title: My all time fav moisturizers!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Sup lovelies! I know I had to make y'll wait for a long time for this video but it's finally here🤩🤩 
.
I have not used moisturizers almost all my life thinking I have enough oil on my skin and perhaps that's one of the most prominent reasons why my skin had to suffer a lot. In this video I spoke about moisturizers that are my holy grail. I completely swear by these💙
.
@cetaphil_india Daily Advance Ultra Hydrating Lotion (all skin types)
@neutrogena.india hydro boost water gel (oily to combination skin)
@pondsindia super light gel (oily skin type)
.
None of these moisturizers feel heavy on the skin and worth every penny. Please feel free to either DM me or drop a comment if you face any specific skin related concern. I'm not a dermatologist but have done my fair share of research and will be happy to help! 
Much love.
.
.
.

@zara
.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Skincare series Part - 1

I have battled with acnes for as long as I can remember. I have even visited dermatologists a couple of times which got me acquainted with acnes on and off. Now that I have finally curated a skin care regimen (oily skin type/acne prone), I'm sharing all these gem of a products with y'll.  I hope this skincare routine can heal your skin as well.  In this video, I spoke about the first step in the skincare process which is using a cleanser, I use @sebamedindia cleansing foam for acne prone and sensitive skin.

latestPosts.caption:
How do I explain this feeling? 

It’s a mixture of emotions, you feel excited with the adrenaline pumping, anxious during the flight at 13,000ft, scared during the first three seconds of the jump, extremely exhilarated during the drop and ultimately elevated when you land 🪂

I remember having tears in my eyes when the parachute became stable and all I could see was the gorgeous palm view 🌴

@hiiii_saiii my love, thanks for gifting me the experience of lifetime ♥️

#skydive #skydivedubai

365 ❤️

Feels like I’ve known this boy forever and still every day feels like a new day ✨

Same love, same passion, same desire to try new adventures, same respect for each other as day 1 🕊️

Can’t wait to experience what next year has in store for us. 

Ps: Don’t miss this beautiful infinity pool experience if you are visiting Dubai, the view is breathtaking 🤌🏼

Love xx
